\c 87
\s Mbiri yeZioni
\d Pisarema ravanakomana vaKora; rwiyo.
\p
\v 1 Nheyo dzake dziri pamakomo matsvene.
\v 2 Jehovha anoda masuo elioni Kupfuura pose panogara Jakobho.
\v 3 Zvinhu zvakanakisa zvinotaurwa pamusoro pako, Iwe guta raMwari.
\v 4 Rahabhi neBhabhironi ndichati vari pakati pavanondiziva; "Tarirai, Firisitia, neTire, neItiopia; Munhu uyu akazvarirwako."
\v 5 Zvirokwazvo, pamusoro pelioni vachati, "Uyu nouyo vakazvarirwamo; Naiye Wokumusorosoro amene acharisimbisa." achaverenga, pakunyora kwake ndudzi, achiti, "Munhu uyu akazvarirwako."
\v 7 Vanoimba navanotamba, vachati,
\s "Matsime angu ose ari mauri."
